dvice. The aim is to show code and get feedback that can enhance everyones knowledge on how to approach design and implementation using a Node approach.</p>\n<p>Agenda for August:</p>\n<p>5-10 minute lightning talk (news, heard of a new library, node in prod etc). Please apply</p>\n<p>20 minute presentation  - Arjun on Promises in node.</p>\n<p>30 minutes code review (open - questions on code you are writing, get feedback on some code)</p>\n<p>Pizza and drinks will be provided by Entelect.</p>\n','2016-08-23','18:00:00',NULL,'Gauteng','Johannesburg','Birnam','3 Melrose Blvd, Johannesburg, 2196, South Africa','-26.1352334','28.06837519999999','https://maps.google.com/?q=3+Melrose+Blvd,+Johannesburg,+2196,+South+Africa&ftid=0x1e950d1dcbc8f5c5:0x26c279220c3f0166','http://www.meetup.com/Jozi-Node-JS/events/233119146',465,'2016-08-16 06:03:56',NULL,'2017-12-13 20:00:06'),(48,1,'September Meetup','september-meetup','info@nodeza.co.za','','Jozi.Node.JS September Meetup','Jozi.Node.JS September Meetup','<p>Jozi.Node.JS September Meetup</p>\n','2016-09-21','18:00:00',NULL,'Gauteng','Johannesburg','Birnam','3 Melrose Blvd, Johannesburg, 2196, South Africa','-26.1352334','28.06837519999999','https://maps.google.com/?q=3+Melrose+Blvd,+Johannesburg,+2196,+South+Africa&ftid=0x1e950d1dcbc8f5c5:0x26c279220c3f0166','http://www.meetup.com/Jozi-Node-JS/events/233119171',437,'2016-09-18 03:55:40',NULL,'2017-12-13 01:09:38'),(49,1,'Testing in Meteor & Stories from the Trenches','testing-in-meteor-stories-from-the-trenches','info@nodeza.co.za','','Finally we\'re back, and this month we\'ll be talking about testing, followed by a little show and tell, we\'d love to hear about y','Finally we\'re back, and this month we\'ll be talking about testing, followed by a little show and tell, we\'d love to hear about your latest or favourite Meteor Project.\r\n\r\nLet us know if you\'re interested in presenting some of your work we\'d love to see it.','<p>Finally we\'re back, and this month we\'ll 