INSERT INTO `meetups` VALUES (1,1,'Johann Detoit','Node.js Cape Town','node-js-cape-town','none@none.com','','We try to meet each month on the third week. Each month we\'ll have a group discussion on a particular aspect of NodeJS, using it','Thanks to the brilliant work of Ryan Dahl, we have node.js, a beautiful and elegant server-side framework built on top of Google\'s V8 Javascript engine. This opens up a whole new world of possibility for developing web apps, APIs, and lightweight HTTP servers.\r\n\r\nWe try to meet each month on the third week. Each month we\'ll have a group discussion on a particular aspect of NodeJS, using it to build apps and any tools or workflows based on it.\r\n\r\nIf you\'d like to present, please send a note with your topic. If you have a suggestion for a topic, feel free to submit it.\r\n\r\nWe are always looking for spaces to use for the meetups. If you\'d like to offer a space for us to use, please reach out to us.','<p>Thanks to the brilliant work of Ryan Dahl, we have node.js, a beautiful and elegant server-side framework built on top of Google\'s V8 Javascript engine. This opens up a whole new world of possibility for developing web apps, APIs, and lightweight HTTP servers.</p>\n<p>We try to meet each month on the third week. Each month we\'ll have a group discussion on a particular aspect of NodeJS, using it to build apps and any tools or workflows based on it.</p>\n<p>If you\'d like to present, please send a note with your topic. If you have a suggestion for a topic, feel free to submit it.</p>\n<p>We are always looking for spaces to use for the meetups. If you\'d like to offer a space for us to use, please reach out to us.</p>\n','Last week of the month','Western Cape','Cape Town','','Old Castle Brewery, Beach Rd, Woodstock, Cape Town, 7915, South Africa','-33.9248885','18.44773609999993','https://maps.google.com/?q=Old+Castle+Brewery&ftid=0x1dcc5d99a8bcd1cb:0x76681ae213743dc1','http://www.meetup.com/nodecpt',2134,'image_1406633822178.jpeg','2014-10-27 13:56:55',1,'2017-12-12 21:15:24'),(2,1,'Len Weister','Jozi.Node.JS','jozi-node-js','none@none.com','','Come and find out about Node.js the awesome server side development environment. All welcome.','Come and find out about Node.js the awesome server side development environment. All welcome.','<p>Come and find out about Node.js the awesome server side development environment. All welcome.</p>\n','Last week of the month','Gauteng','Johannesburg','','44 Stanley Ave, Johannesburg, 2092, South Africa','-26.18547','28.019019999999955','https://maps.google.com/?q=44+Stanley+Ave,+Johannesburg,+2092,+South+Africa&ftid=0x1e950c0a7a180075:0xabc336394e358c99',NULL,1222,'image_1415495927344.png','2014-10-27 13:56:55',1,'2017-12-12 21:15:22'),(3,1,'Andre Vermeulen','Cape Town Nodebots','cape-town-nodebots','andre@gmail.com','0724038759','Calling all Cape Town (aspiring) hardware hackers! We use Javascript to move more than just DIVs. ','Calling all Cape Town (aspiring) hardware hackers! We use Javascript to move more than just DIVs. For those interested in hacking hardware using Javascript. If you want to built a robot, but don\'t know where to start, this is for you. Or maybe you are an old Arduino hand trying something new or want to teach others a few ticks. Alternatively you can just come to show off your latest bot...','<p>Calling all Cape Town (aspiring) hardware hackers! We use Javascript to move more than just DIVs. For those interested in hacking hardware using Javascript. If you want to built a robot, but don\'t know where to start, this is for you. Or maybe you are an old Arduino hand trying something new or want to teach others a few ticks. Alternatively you can just come to show off your latest bot...</p>\n','Once every month','Western Cape','Cape Town','Woodstock','Woodstock, Cape Town, South Africa','-33.930556','18.44722200000001','https://maps.google.com/maps/place?q=Woodstock,+Cape+Town,+South+Africa&ftid=0x1dcc5da25b1b83cb:0x9528ebc70c50cb86',NULL,795,'image_1445508604273.jpg','2014-11-09 20:24:49',1,'2017-12-12 21:15:20'),(4,1,'Alice Yu, Jade Wang, Michael Prins','Meteor Cape Town','meteor-cape-town','jaco@productive.me','','Meet other developers using Meteor. Share your knowledge, apps, and get feedback from others. ','Meet other developers using Meteor. Share your knowledge, apps, and get feedback from others. Meteor is an open-source platform for building top-quality web apps in a fraction of the time, whether you\'re an expert developer or just getting started.','<p>Meet other developers using Meteor. Share your knowledge, apps, and get feedback from others. Meteor is an open-source platform for building top-quality web apps in a fraction of the time, whether you\'re an expert developer or just getting started.</p>\n','Once every month','Western Cape','Cape Town','Cape Town','3 Ravenscraig Rd, Woodstock, Cape Town, 7915, South Africa','-33.9296553','18.443542699999966','https://maps.google.com/maps/place?q=3+Ravenscraig+Rd,+Woodstock,+Cape+Town,+7915,+South+Africa&ftid=0x1dcc5d9c697d1ffd:0xc5007595d81ab65','http://www.meetup.com/Meteor-Cape-Town',680,'image_1445508741866.jpg','2015-02-03 13:27:42',1,'2017-12-12 21:15:19'),(5,1,'Alice Yu','Meteo Johannesburg','meteo-johannesburg','info@nodeza.co.za','0724038759','Meet other developers using Meteor. Share your knowledge, apps, and get feedback from others.','Meet other developers using Meteor. Share your knowledge, apps, and get feedback from others.\r\n\r\nMeteor is an open-source platform for building top-quality web apps in a fraction of the time, whether you\'re an expert developer or just getting started.','<p>Meet other developers using Meteor. Share your knowledge, apps, and get feedback from others.</p>\n<p>Meteor is an open-source platform for building top-quality web apps in a fraction of the time, whether you\'re an expert developer or just getting started.</p>\n','Once every month','Gauteng','Johannesburg','Jozi','Johannesburg, S